===Etymology===
[[File:Christian Boers Pirataatak 1769 cr No 3.jpg|thumb|A 1769 drawing of a xebec used by [[Algeria]]n [[pirate#Noun|pirates]] by [[w:no:Christian Børs (sjømann)|Christian Børs]], a [[sailor]] from [[Bergen]], [[Norway]], who was taken prisoner in Algeria]]
From {{der|en|fr|chebec}}, from {{der|en|es|jabeque|xabeque}} or {{der|en|ca|xabec}} or {{der|en|it|sciabecco}}, from {{der|en|ar|شُبَّاك|t=fishing-net}}. Not to confuse with the {{m|en|sambuq}}, an [[Indian Ocean|Indian-Sea]] vessel.
