===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A small two-[[mast#Noun|masted]], and later three-masted, [[Mediterranean]] [[transport]] [[ship#Noun|ship]] with an [[overhanging#Adjective|overhanging]] [[bow#Noun|bow]] and [[stern#Noun|stern]]. {{defdate|from mid 18th c.}}
